    <section class="legal-section">
        <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">

            <div id="privacy" class="legal-block legal-anchor">
                <h4>Privacy Policy</h4>
                <p>This Privacy Policy describes how Premier Auto Garage ("we", "us", or "our") collects and processes your personal data in accordance with the UK General Data Protection Regulation (UK GDPR) and the Data Protection Act 2018. We collect personal information provided directly via our contact form or telephone, including your name, phone number, postcode, email and vehicle details. This information is used solely for the purpose of providing repair quotations, scheduling service appointments, and fulfilling your booking in London.</p>
                <br>
                <p><strong>Maps:</strong> Our website uses OpenStreetMap via the Leaflet library to display our service area. Map imagery is retrieved directly from OpenStreetMap servers. No personal data is transmitted to OpenStreetMap, and no tracking cookies are set by this feature.</p>
                <br>
                <p><strong>Data Sharing:</strong> We do not sell your data to third parties. Your information will never be used for marketing purposes without your explicit consent, and we will retain it only for as long as necessary to fulfil your service request and comply with our legal obligations.</p>
            </div>

            <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;">

            <div id="terms" class="legal-block legal-anchor">
                <h4>Terms &amp; Conditions</h4>
                <p><strong>1. Estimates:</strong> All estimates and quotations are based on a preliminary inspection or description of the fault. If additional faults are discovered during the course of repair, we will contact you immediately with a revised written estimate before any further work is carried out.</p>
                <p><strong>2. Payment:</strong> Payment in full is due upon satisfactory completion of all work. We accept all major credit and debit cards, bank transfer, and cash. For orders of specialist or high-value parts, a deposit may be required prior to ordering.</p>
                <p><strong>3. Cancellations:</strong> We request a minimum of 24 hours' notice for any cancellation or rescheduling. Failure to provide adequate notice may result in a standard administration fee being applied to your account.</p>
                <p><strong>4. Guarantee:</strong> All workmanship carried out by Premier Auto Garage is guaranteed for 12 months or 12,000 miles, whichever comes first. Parts are covered by the relevant manufacturer's warranty. This guarantee does not affect your statutory rights.</p>
            </div>

            <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;">

            <div id="cookies" class="legal-block legal-anchor">
                <h4>Cookie Policy</h4>
                <p>This website is designed to be lightweight and respectful of your privacy. We do not use third-party tracking cookies, analytics scripts, or advertising pixels. The only cookies that may be present are strictly essential technical cookies required for the correct operation of the website, such as form submission security tokens. These do not require prior consent under current UK regulations.</p>
            </div>

        </div>
